A simple yet powerful Flask-based Notes Web Application where you can add, edit, and delete notes with flash message alerts for better user experience.
Built with ❤️ using Python (Flask), SqlLite, HTML, CSS, and a sprinkle of ChatGPT magic.



notes-app/
│
├── static/
│   └── style.css        # Stylesheet (designed with ChatGPT's help)
│
├── templates/
│   ├── home.html        # Homepage with list of notes
│   ├── add_note.html    # Add note page
│   ├── edit_note.html   # Edit note page
│
├── app.py               # Main Flask application
├── models.py            # Database models
├── requirements.txt     # Python dependencies
└── README.md            # Project documentation
